title: Erm still in placements 121 wins and 101 losses, i was B1 last night
body: Explain please, i played ranked last night and it displayed as B1, but now it says placements even though i have 121 wins and 101 losses

replies.body:
There's currently a [bug](http://status.leagueoflegends.com/?en_AU#oce) where Leagues tab information is not displaying correctly. Don't worry there haven't been any changes to you rank.

Sorry about that ;)
